summary: A Sakura Haruno Preset for Racemenu.
descriptionHtml: Hi Guys I made this preset for my friend who loves sakura from naruto. I'm not new to nexus or modding, but I am new to kind of making my own Presets. This Preset is pretty simple and results will vary for your skin texture. It's made for the cbbe body (slim), and requires 12femalebrowsesp from http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/? by HHaley, http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11173/? by itamukun, and http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49963/? by jimtownirish.
author: Valdaus
